** ER
E-01 UPDATE OPTION SHOULD BE 0, 1 OR 2!
E-02 ENTER CUSTOMER CODE!
E-03 ENTER DELIVERY CODE!
E-04 ENTER FACTORY!
E-05 DELIVERY CODE NOT FOUND IN PACKING LIST OPTION!
E-06 ENTER DOCK CODE!
E-07 XXX
E-08 ENTER PICK-UP DATE!
E-09 PICK-UP DATE (YYMMDD) IS INVALID!
E-10 XXX
E-11 XXX
E-12 <ADD> ORDER EXISTS ALREADY!
E-13 <CHANGE> ORDER DOES NOT EXIST!
E-14 <CHANGE> ORDER WAS CANCELLED ALREADY!
E-15 <CANCEL> ORDER DOES NOT EXIST!
E-16 <CANCEL> ORDER WAS CANCELLED ALREADY!
E-17 ENTER QUANTITY!
E-18 ENTER ORDER#
E-19 ENTER KANBAN#
E-20 SALES BILLED DATE (YYMMDD) IS INVALID!
E-21 CARD SHOULD BE M390, M391 OR MA02!
E-22 ENTER USER QTY/CNT!
E-23 CUSTOMER CODE ERROR!
E-24 DELIVERY CODE ERROR!
E-25 ENTER FACTORY!
E-26 NO DATA IN SHIPMENT MASTER!
E-27 CUSTOMER IS < 0541 >
E-28 CUSTOMER IS < 3411 >
E-29 PART# DOES NOT EXIST IN PART MASTER
E-30 ENTER LINE FEED!
E-31 ENTER BIN#
E-32 REASON CODE ERROR!
E-33 ORDER CODE ERROR!
E-34 RELEASED DATE ERROR!
E-35 ENTER RESERVE LOCATION!
E-36 ENTER FORD PGM ID!
E-37 KBAN & PRT# NOT MATCHED IN USR KBAN M/F. IF OK HIT ENTR
E-38 ENTER WAREHOUSE LOCATION!
E-39 ENTER FIT LOCATION
W-40 IF YOU WANT TO ADD THIS ORDER, PRESS F7 AGAIN!
E-41 MOVE CURSOR ONTO CORRECT LINE!
E-42 PART# IS DUPLICATE!
E-43 DO NOT ERASE PART#
E-44 USER QTY/BOX SHOULD BE SAME AS IAF QTY/BOX!
E-45 QTY SHOULD BE MULTIPLE OF QTY/BOX!
E-46 THIS ORDER HAS BEEN POSTED TO SALES ALREADY!
W-47 CHECK PICK UP DATE! IF IT IS CORRECT, PRESS ENTER!
E-48 KBAN & PART# NOT MATCHED IN USR KBAN MASTER!
E-49 SYMBOL CODE SHOULD BE D, P OR BLANK!
E-50 P OR R IS NOT ALLOWED FOR FORD PART, PLEASE SEE PC COORDINATOR!
E-51 TESLA INVOICE#(MANIFEST#) SHOULD NOT BE BLANK!
E-52 TTAI'S DOCK CODE SHOULD BE "1"
E-53 TTAI'S ORDER# SHOULD BE 7569!
